00:02:26.793 --> 00:02:35.192
I told you all the experience I had with the Lord at His crucifixion and Him talking to me about being healed.

00:02:35.193 --> 00:02:40.990
I believe with all my heart. I don't doubt in my heart about anything.

00:02:40.991 --> 00:02:47.157
I believe by faith that I call those things that be not as though they were.

00:02:47.158 --> 00:02:57.116
We call ourselves healed, whole, and well as we grow our faith and get in the Word more because we know the truth and the truth has set us free.

00:02:57.117 --> 00:03:08.653
It will be in every area of your life. If you have a foundation of the Word of God inside of you, no matter what your circumstance, it will change your circumstances.

00:03:08.654 --> 00:03:15.540
I believe that Jesus Christ is the healer. I believe it with all my heart in every area.

00:03:15.541 --> 00:03:21.679
No matter what, I'm not moved by what I see. As I'm overcoming this cough, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:30.899
I'm not moved by what I feel: congestion. I'm not moved by what the devil tries to throw at me. I'm moved by what the Word says. It's foundation.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:44.857
He said in His Word, regardless of the cough, regardless of congestion or whatever, 'By His stripes, I am healed.'That is foundation, and that settles it.

00:03:44.858 --> 00:03:55.245
I'm not moved by what the circumstances say. If you're moved by what your flesh is telling you every single day, you're going to be moved by the circumstances.

00:03:55.246 --> 00:04:04.971
But you have to have your foot and your foundation planted on the Word of God and say, 'This flesh is not moving me.

00:04:04.972 --> 00:04:17.329
I see what the Bible says and I believe what the Bible says regardless of my circumstances.'It's foundation.

00:04:17.330 --> 00:04:23.088
That's why I tell you, you may be hurting financially. I take a financial seed.

00:04:23.089 --> 00:04:28.848
Every time we have a need, we sow a seed. People don't understand that, but I believe in seed faith.

00:04:28.849 --> 00:04:35.359
I believe if you have a need, just like a farmer, you go out and you plant the seed. That's what we do.

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:51.186
We'll go out and say, 'Okay, well, we'll put a $100 here or whatever.'We sow that $100 and believe by faith that God's going to provide through supernatural income, that He'll give us an idea or He'll anoint us to do something.

00:04:51.187 --> 00:05:01.055
He'll give us favor. The Lord gives you favor. I believe a day of favor is worth more than a thousand days of working hard.

00:05:01.056 --> 00:05:08.700
All you need is a day of favor and the hand of the Lord moving favor in your life in every area if you just believe Him for it.

00:05:08.701 --> 00:05:15.043
But it takes you stepping out of the boat and walking on the water with Him for Him to come through.

00:05:15.044 --> 00:05:25.918
A lot of times it takes sacrificial things. He wants to see, 'How important am I to you? Do you have a hunger for me?

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:36.932
Is it just lip service?'A lot of times we say a lot, but do we do what He asks us to do in His Word?

00:05:36.933 --> 00:05:40.989
Do we obey Him? Do we witness to our brother? Do we pray for him?

00:05:40.990 --> 00:05:51.286
Do we show the love of God to people when they're mean to us? Regardless of how they treat us, we're to operate in love.

00:05:51.287 --> 00:06:00.996
A lot of times that's not easy because our flesh gets all upset because we want to just say something bad back to them or do something stupid.

00:06:00.997 --> 00:06:08.253
You get off in the flesh and the devil gets a hold of you. That's where you have to stay in the law of love.

00:06:08.254 --> 00:06:16.914
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong. That's right. I have to practice it too. Every day I have to practice in the comment section.

00:06:16.915 --> 00:06:23.434
My son tells me somebody says something mean, and I say, 'Oh, we just love them.'We're not going to be moved by that.

00:06:23.435 --> 00:06:32.299
It's not them; they have a devil. They've got some kind of demonic spirit bothering them and that's why they retaliate the way they do. That's what you have to do.

00:06:32.300 --> 00:06:50.084
