00:06:50.085 --> 00:06:58.274
You have to say, 'Hey, I choose today to walk in love toward my wife, my children, and anybody who might try to tip my mood.

00:06:58.274 --> 00:07:04.103
I'm going to walk in love. I'm going to walk in love because faith works by love.

00:07:04.104 --> 00:07:23.345
If you're not walking in love and you don't see your faith producing something, if you don't see results in your faith every single day, you have to say, 'Where's my love walk?'because faith works by love because God is love.

00:07:23.346 --> 00:07:36.113
If you're not having faith move your mountain in your area for healing or demonstrations and manifestations of the glory—if you're not experiencing the fresh presence of the Lord every day in your life—you've got to check your love walk.

00:07:36.114 --> 00:07:40.105
How am I treating others around me? Because God is love, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:40.106 --> 00:07:49.300
He dwells in us and we dwell in Him. He is in us, and I am seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:07:49.301 --> 00:08:03.674
If you're in strife all the time, check your love walk. Check your love walk concerning your finances. Check your fear level.

00:08:03.675 --> 00:08:13.758
Check your sowing level, how you're giving and believing every day for what you're wanting the Lord to be a part of your finances.

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:25.331
When you sow a seed, God will make you reap. For every seed you sow, I believe some thirty, sixty, or a hundred-fold.

00:08:25.332 --> 00:08:31.902
