00:08:40.968 --> 00:08:50.830
I take the seed of $100 and I say, 'I sow this seed, Father, in a direction toward what I'm believing for.'I'm believing, Father, for a creative idea to pay off the car.

00:08:50.831 --> 00:08:55.199
