00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:24.370
I've got a mansion for you when you come home.'You say, 'Well, I don't want any of that over here because it might ruin me.'You better work on your character then, because I'm telling you, God wants you to have exceedingly, abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

